data.description: Welcome home charming property nestled in a well-established neighborhood! This home boasts 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, making it ideal for growing or those who love to entertain. With four well sized bedrooms, there's ample space for everyone in the family. The 2.5 bathrooms ensure convenience for your daily routines and guests. Situated on an oversized 13,000 square foot corner lot, this property offers plenty of outdoor space for various activities and landscaping possibilities. In the newly carpeted upstairs you'll find a den and game room, along with 3 bedrooms providing flexible spaces for work, play, or relaxation offering a fresh and cozy atmosphere. The extra-large garage is perfect for storing vehicles or boats, as well as additional storage space for tools and equipment.    This home offers the perfect blend of space, comfort, and convenience in a desirable neighborhood. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own!
